Privacy Policy
DropForge is owned by Bilsoft AB.
We use this Privacy Policy, which sets out how we process the information collected by DropForge, as well as the reasons why we must collect certain personal data about you. Therefore, you should read this Privacy Policy before using DropForge.
We care about your personal data and guarantee its confidentiality and security.
Personal information we collect:
When using DropForge, we do not collect information about your device, including information about your web browser, IP address, time zone, etc.
We do not collect personal data that you use when using DropForge.
How do we process your data?
Our top priority is customer safety, which is why we do not collect any information about the DropForge user.
You can use DropForge without telling us who you are or revealing any information by which anyone could identify you as a specific individual. You can choose not to provide us with your personal information.
Content Rights:
DropForge does not host, display, or have access to third-party content.
Legal Disclosure:
We will disclose any information we receive if required or permitted to do so by law, such as to comply with a subpoena or similar legal process, and when we believe in good faith that disclosure is necessary to protect our rights, protect your safety or the safety of others, investigate fraud, or respond to a government request.
Contact Information:
If you would like to contact us to learn more about this Policy or would like to contact us regarding any matter relating to individual rights and your Personal Information, you may send an email to shelkoplyasov.sergey@gmail.com.
